node.text: Everything lies within the details. Our Italian leather soles are lacquered in the perfect shade of deep nude and we were never going to diminish their flawless beauty with unsightly protectors. Our sandals now feature tiny pale-gold metal sole tips to help protect the leather in the most needed area.

node.text:
‘Sesso’ in colour ‘Aurum’, a summer evening dream. 

Beyond barely there, the Sesso with its refined, feminine aesthetic, takes sex appeal in a sandal, to its pinnacle. Featuring ultra slim lace strapping, vertiginous solid steel spike heels, shimmering kid leather and 9ct gold plated hardware.

Details-

Pale gold metallic kid leather upper and laces
9ct gold plated toe points and lace tips
Nude glacé kid leather insole
Nude lacquered leather outsole
120mm ultra thin kid leather covered solid steel heel
Fits true to size
Handmade in London
